6,0.01847978,-0.00527021,0.01196362,0.03258611,0.0490048,-0.00837883,-0.05960362,0.01305865,0.02469489,0.05101533,-0.05645873,-0.01671883,-0.05088848,-0.06039394,0.0546659,-0.04620926,-0.00792487,-0.00237028,-0.0339572,0.01409186,0.07244615,0.06249022,-0.03231025,-0.0358468,-0.04395394,0.03789451,-0.04889945,-0.00937571,0.05775246,-0.01280477,0.01928995,0.03918197,0.09604713,-0.00285506,-0.02075369,0.03139839,0.02166045,-0.04573424,-0.04911302,0.03614448,0.07777474,0.05978046],"last_embed":{"hash":"17c3da062aaa7c63233d2978409f7f564ed0737717a640e3dfbb7716e063024d","tokens":472}}},"last_read":{"hash":"17c3da062aaa7c63233d2978409f7f564ed0737717a640e3dfbb7716e063024d","at":1744796450600},"class_name":"SmartSource","last_import":{"mtime":1744414975635,"size":51462,"at":1744796448328,"hash":"17c3da062aaa7c63233d2978409f7f564ed0737717a640e3dfbb7716e063024d"},"blocks":{"#---frontmatter---":[1,8],"#Interview with Koffin Kats":[10,492],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#{1}":[12,245],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Pressing Play and Doing Some Talking.":[246,249],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Pressing Play and Doing Some Talking.#{1}":[248,249],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#I Think it Was a Bit Different over Here, because We Are like This Big ***Making Pinchy Gesture with fingers***, and America's Huge, so We Had, in the Fifties, Sixties, We just Had [FM radio](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/FM_broadcasting_in_the_UK), so You Could Sit in Your Little Studio in London and Reach the Whole Country. So I Think We didn’t Have such a Range of Radio Stations and Personalities and Stuff.":[250,253],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#I Think it Was a Bit Different over Here, because We Are like This Big ***Making Pinchy Gesture with fingers***, and America's Huge, so We Had, in the Fifties, Sixties, We just Had [FM radio](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/FM_broadcasting_in_the_UK), so You Could Sit in Your Little Studio in London and Reach the Whole Country. So I Think We didn’t Have such a Range of Radio Stations and Personalities and Stuff.#{1}":[252,253],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#I Spose We Had the Pirate Radio Thing, People in Little Boats, Broadcasting from International Waters or Whatever.":[254,257],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#I Spose We Had the Pirate Radio Thing, People in Little Boats, Broadcasting from International Waters or Whatever.#{1}":[256,257],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#So, Yeah. I Think Our Radio's a Bit Different over Here!":[258,261],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#So, Yeah. I Think Our Radio's a Bit Different over Here!#{1}":[260,261],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#I Get the General Idea, Yeah. Now there Are Very Few Shows that Run on the Actual Radio that Are Worth Listening To. With the Internet, Internet Radio is a Big Thing Now. I Think it Tends to Be Very Specialized, like if You Know what you’re Looking For, You Can just Go and Be like \"I just want to Listen to psychobilly\" or Whatever. And that’s All You'll Get and You Won't Get that Random Song I Guess. You Lose Some of that Chance Discoverability. Anyway, John, how Are You Fitting into the Band?":[262,266],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#I Get the General Idea, Yeah. Now there Are Very Few Shows that Run on the Actual Radio that Are Worth Listening To. With the Internet, Internet Radio is a Big Thing Now. I Think it Tends to Be Very Specialized, like if You Know what you’re Looking For, You Can just Go and Be like \"I just want to Listen to psychobilly\" or Whatever. And that’s All You'll Get and You Won't Get that Random Song I Guess. You Lose Some of that Chance Discoverability. Anyway, John, how Are You Fitting into the Band?#{1}":[264,266],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#That’s What People Do! There’s a Difference between Getting along with Someone to Talk to for like Half an Hour...":[267,276],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#That’s What People Do! There’s a Difference between Getting along with Someone to Talk to for like Half an Hour...#{1}":[269,276],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#That Could Be Really Cool Though, because You'll Always Have Different Influences from Someone That's a \"psychobilly guitarist\".":[277,286],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#That Could Be Really Cool Though, because You'll Always Have Different Influences from Someone That's a \"psychobilly guitarist\".#{1}":[279,286],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Are You Still Practicing Everyday or Have You Got it down to the Point-":[287,291],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Are You Still Practicing Everyday or Have You Got it down to the Point-#{1}":[289,291],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#That Reminds Me of a [podcast](http://www.merlinmann.com/roderick/ep-24-the-wrong-mustache.html) with John Roderick, from The Long Winters. He Played Bass for Harvey Danger for a While. I Think He Blagged His way in because Their Bass Player Got Pneumonia and They Were Supposed to Go and Play on Some TV Show and so He Learnt that One Song They Were Going to Play.":[292,295],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#That Reminds Me of a [podcast](http://www.merlinmann.com/roderick/ep-24-the-wrong-mustache.html) with John Roderick, from The Long Winters. He Played Bass for Harvey Danger for a While. I Think He Blagged His way in because Their Bass Player Got Pneumonia and They Were Supposed to Go and Play on Some TV Show and so He Learnt that One Song They Were Going to Play.#{1}":[294,295],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Yeah, Probably, and then He Said the First time He Ever Played through an Amp Was on that Show. They Got There, the Stage Manager Was like “Your Amp is over there” and He Went and Plugged In, Hit a Few Notes to Test it Out, then the Guy is like [\"we're live in five, four....\"](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l_lhJSLvlQc) (seriously, Click that Link if only for the Unspoken Conversation just after the 2 Minute Mark. \"You're Playing bass!\"--\"I know!\")":[296,301],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Yeah, Probably, and then He Said the First time He Ever Played through an Amp Was on that Show. They Got There, the Stage Manager Was like “Your Amp is over there” and He Went and Plugged In, Hit a Few Notes to Test it Out, then the Guy is like [\"we're live in five, four....\"](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l_lhJSLvlQc) (seriously, Click that Link if only for the Unspoken Conversation just after the 2 Minute Mark. \"You're Playing bass!\"--\"I know!\")#{1}":[298,301],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#And He Plays the Song, Doing Proper Backing Vocals and Everything! After that They Were on Tour and He Was Running through the Set Every Night *after* the Gig, and Working on it in the Day time before the Gig, and after a Couple Weeks he’s like \"I Know what I'm Doing Now, I Don't Need to Practice it today.\" and then that Night just Sucked! He Didn't Have a Clue what to Play.":[302,305],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#And He Plays the Song, Doing Proper Backing Vocals and Everything! After that They Were on Tour and He Was Running through the Set Every Night *after* the Gig, and Working on it in the Day time before the Gig, and after a Couple Weeks he’s like \"I Know what I'm Doing Now, I Don't Need to Practice it today.\" and then that Night just Sucked! He Didn't Have a Clue what to Play.#{1}":[304,305],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#And you’ve Got the [solo album](https://soundcloud.com/therealjohnkay) Coming up or Something, Right?":[306,309],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#And you’ve Got the [solo album](https://soundcloud.com/therealjohnkay) Coming up or Something, Right?#{1}":[308,309],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Did You Have other People Playing on it or is it like a Nine Inch Nails/Foo Fighters Job where You're Doing Everything?":[310,313],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Did You Have other People Playing on it or is it like a Nine Inch Nails/Foo Fighters Job where You're Doing Everything?#{1}":[312,313],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Cool, I'm Looking forward to It.":[314,317],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Cool, I'm Looking forward to It.#{1}":[316,317],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Stage Show, because You Guys Put on One Hell of a Show, Do You Have to Practice that a Lot Too?":[318,333],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Stage Show, because You Guys Put on One Hell of a Show, Do You Have to Practice that a Lot Too?#{1}":[320,333],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Like Last Year, when We Played at the [Lady Luck](http://theladyluck.co.uk), Ian Nearly Got the Bass in His Face a Few Times. He's just Casually Turning His Head as a Big Lump of Wood Passes through the Air His Face Was Occupying a Split Second Ago.":[334,337],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Like Last Year, when We Played at the [Lady Luck](http://theladyluck.co.uk), Ian Nearly Got the Bass in His Face a Few Times. He's just Casually Turning His Head as a Big Lump of Wood Passes through the Air His Face Was Occupying a Split Second Ago.#{1}":[336,337],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Are there Good and Bad Places to Play At? What’s the Best and Worst Experience You've Had?":[338,349],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Are there Good and Bad Places to Play At? What’s the Best and Worst Experience You've Had?#{1}":[340,349],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Do You Still Get the Sound Guy Saying \"there’s a Weird Clicking Sound Coming from the bass\"?":[350,355],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Do You Still Get the Sound Guy Saying \"there’s a Weird Clicking Sound Coming from the bass\"?#{1}":[352,355],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#It’s Like “No that’s fine.....\"":[356,357],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Cheesy Interview Question Alert! If You Were Stuck on a Desert Island-":[358,363],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Cheesy Interview Question Alert! If You Were Stuck on a Desert Island-#{1}":[360,363],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#You're Stuck on the Island, You Have to Choose One Kind of Food and One Kind of Drink and like an Album and Book or Something, what Are You Going to Bring?":[364,367],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#You're Stuck on the Island, You Have to Choose One Kind of Food and One Kind of Drink and like an Album and Book or Something, what Are You Going to Bring?#{1}":[366,367],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Plenty of Water. Let's Say There's a River.":[368,373],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Plenty of Water. Let's Say There's a River.#{1}":[370,373],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#An Old lady’s Leg?":[374,377],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#An Old lady’s Leg?#{1}":[376,377],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#What Would You Have to Read and Listen To?":[378,387],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#What Would You Have to Read and Listen To?#{1}":[380,387],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Have You Read [The Dark Tower](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Dark_Tower_(series) )?":[388,391],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Have You Read [The Dark Tower](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Dark_Tower_(series) )?#{1}":[390,391],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#A Couple of Months ago I Finished the Last One, it Takes a While!":[392,395],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#A Couple of Months ago I Finished the Last One, it Takes a While!#{1}":[394,395],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Totally.":[396,399],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Totally.#{1}":[398,399],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#John, Same Thing.":[400,403],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#John, Same Thing.#{1}":[402,403],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Good Choice.":[404,411],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Good Choice.#{1}":[406,411],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Oh, I Read One of Those I Think, Gai-jin?":[412,419],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Oh, I Read One of Those I Think, Gai-jin?#{1}":[414,419],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Sorted. You’re Always like Super Busy, Any Nerdy Computer Stuff You Do to Keep Organized? Or Do You Leave that to the Man downstairs with [the beard](https://www.facebook.com/rok.fatov?fref=ts)?":[420,427],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Sorted. You’re Always like Super Busy, Any Nerdy Computer Stuff You Do to Keep Organized? Or Do You Leave that to the Man downstairs with [the beard](https://www.facebook.com/rok.fatov?fref=ts)?#{1}":[422,427],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Kinda Almost like Being on a Desert Island....":[428,431],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Kinda Almost like Being on a Desert Island....#{1}":[430,431],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#When's the next Album Out? Is the next Album You Three?":[432,439],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#When's the next Album Out? Is the next Album You Three?#{1}":[434,439],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Squeezing in time between Shows.":[440,448],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Squeezing in time between Shows.#{1}":[442,448],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#It's not the Sixties with The Beatles, where They Can just like Have Six Months Studio Time.":[449,454],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#It's not the Sixties with The Beatles, where They Can just like Have Six Months Studio Time.#{1}":[451,454],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#You Think about it Too Much.":[455,461],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#You Think about it Too Much.#{1}":[457,461],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Yea, That's Quite a Common Theme. People Will Say a Bands' First Album is Really Raw and then by Their Third Album It's All Over-produced. I Guess that Can Happen, Better to Bash it out and Get it Done.":[462,465],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Yea, That's Quite a Common Theme. People Will Say a Bands' First Album is Really Raw and then by Their Third Album It's All Over-produced. I Guess that Can Happen, Better to Bash it out and Get it Done.#{1}":[464,465],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Anything Else You want People to Know?":[466,469],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Anything Else You want People to Know?#{1}":[468,469],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Yea, it Seems to Be Getting Updated More Now, You're the Nerdy One?":[470,474],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Yea, it Seems to Be Getting Updated More Now, You're the Nerdy One?#{1}":[472,474],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Yeah that’s like Business Jerks N That.":[475,478],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Yeah that’s like Business Jerks N That.#{1}":[477,478],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Cool. Cheers Guys. I Think that’s about It!":[479,484],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#Cool. Cheers Guys. I Think that’s about It!#{1}":[481,484],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#That Was Nice!":[485,488],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#That Was Nice!#{1}":[487,488],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#I Didn't Really Know what I Was Doing, but that Wasn't Too Bad!":[489,492],"#Interview with Koffin Kats#I Didn't Really Know what I Was Doing, but that Wasn't Too Bad!#{1}":[491,492]},"outlinks":[{"title":"The Koffin Kats","target":"http://koffinkatsrock.com","line":12},{"title":"Koffin Kats at Lady Luck","target":"Koffin Kats at Lady Luck","line":14},{"title":"Koffin Kats, Cowboy and the Corpse at The Louisiana","target":"Koffin Kats, Cowboy and the Corpse at The Louisiana","line":14},{"title":"the second boom of punk rock in the early nineties","target":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Punk_rock#Revival","line":18},{"title":"Reverend Horton Heat","target":"http://www.reverendhortonheat.com","line":19},{"title":"Beavis and Butthead","target":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QlVkr10DaAE","line":19},{"title":"Misfits","target":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Misfits_(band","line":23},{"title":"Ramones","target":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramones","line":23},{"title":"Clash","target":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Clash","line":23},{"title":"brand new cadillac","target":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HvNHXbTL7Oc","line":26},{"title":"The Meteors","target":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OTMAPP","line":30},{"title":"The Long Tall Texans","target":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PSmppsgtlBI","line":30},{"title":"The Peacocks","target":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=suH-sgX6PFc","line":30},{"title":"The Living End","target":"http://www.thelivingend.com","line":32},{"title":"Prisoner of Society","target":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VVtD4qMy5Hc","line":40},{"title":"Johnny Got a Boom Boom","target":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=om9p0NUNlSk","line":42},{"title":"\"John Kay guitarist\"","target":"htt