"smart_blocks:Drafts/KKint final.md#Interview with Koffin Kats#I Get the General Idea, Yeah. Now there Are Very Few Shows that Run on the Actual Radio that Are Worth Listening To. With the Internet, Internet Radio is a Big Thing Now. I Think it Tends to Be Very Specialized, like if You Know what you’re Looking For, You Can just Go and Be like \"I just want to Listen to psychobilly\" or Whatever. And that’s All You'll Get and You Won't Get that Random Song I Guess. You Lose Some of that Chance Discoverability. Anyway, John, how Are You Fitting into the Band?": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.05268269,0.00186907,0.03179442,-0.01921301,0.00900344,0.03124199,0.03106814,0.03620978,-0.02642649,0.00548698,-0.01575913,0.03015818,-0.01741107,0.01310346,0.03311622,-0.01627739,0.03329278,-0.06342582,-0.07219547,0.0493593,-0.01669141,-0.02664607,-0.01817822,-0.00788431,0.04430596,-0.00304409,0.05554643,-0.09556379,-0.0658268,-0.17993441,0.00592585,-0.01929764,0.04737901,-0.04934389,-0.05291587,0.00493448,0.00416123,0.01764694,-0.01895539,0.05674071,0.0392324,0.00226508,0.01667046,-0.02865914,0.04657506,0.01036773,-0.01607304,-0.01006754,0.02821821,-0.01227024,-0.04102937,-0.02214804,0.03027587,0.00164676,0.00912361,0.02005815,0.05962585,0.05410074,0.06058941,0.03947739,0.03775429,0.04798444,-0.19183652,0.06494167,0.01079679,0.0346339,-0.07163551,-0.01593938,-0.0055008,0.03403535,-0.00389434,0.00880813,0.00971426,0.00177507,0.02355699,-0.00144902,0.02414181,0.04737042,-0.0253888,-0.05019557,-0.02201705,0.04440171,-0.05340711,-0.07735861,-0.06684506,-0.02986427,-0.03229336,-0.02541253,-0.01646086,0.06587671,0.01870428,-0.02568777,0.07194172,-0.01058438,-0.02537115,-0.04357797,0.02169959,-0.00770203,-0.02873543,0.08498229,-0.04940681,0.02652013,0.06584468,0.03967862,-0.05515578,-0.04954034,-0.03663383,-0.0794216,0.02339594,-0.03083197,0.0566239,0.03309137,0.00063131,-0.00516339,0.04985838,0.05107749,0.0471017,0.05567137,0.04329929,-0.0027199,0.0280684