"smart_blocks:Drafts/KKint final.md#Interview with Koffin Kats#Yeah, Probably, and then He Said the First time He Ever Played through an Amp Was on that Show. They Got There, the Stage Manager Was like “Your Amp is over there” and He Went and Plugged In, Hit a Few Notes to Test it Out, then the Guy is like [\"we're live in five, four....\"](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l_lhJSLvlQc) (seriously, Click that Link if only for the Unspoken Conversation just after the 2 Minute Mark. \"You're Playing bass!\"--\"I know!\")": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.07459096,0.00333444,0.04282877,-0.04851574,-0.02061832,0.03900196,0.0492293,0.05772553,-0.01215453,0.00688637,-0.03120528,0.01557209,-0.02442832,0.03357393,0.02232236,-0.02935995,0.01019683,-0.02497827,-0.06654684,0.01348386,0.0672057,-0.01440542,0.00319994,-0.033509,0.05053566,-0.05349698,0.0327016,-0.08233342,-0.0596358,-0.2186574,-0.05390433,0.00142666,0.04774337,-0.06424511,-0.05885405,0.00645766,-0.00939615,0.01707485,-0.05743742,0.04620697,0.04505885,-0.02805787,0.02241921,-0.05341547,0.04202641,-0.01710691,-0.02513244,-0.06646061,0.06985605,-0.0302941,-0.02820733,-0.01519174,0.03906485,-0.05182359,0.01483457,0.01248691,0.08319111,0.04520581,0.07008837,0.00239248,0.03315964,0.03628586,-0.20917708,0.07326487,-0.0163567,0.07397915,-0.05274236,-0.05155786,0.02543099,0.05663552,0.02646409,-0.05388679,0.01826246,-0.02581623,0.01758222,-0.03470188,0.02846113,0.03311174,-0.00022105,-0.01201321,-0.00270414,0.01408246,-0.05804286,-0.05998207,-0.08811027,-0.0221756,0.00834721,-0.00475565,-0.01051914,0.04959622,-0.00423179,-0.02599801,0.04313127,-0.04297953,-0.02253416,-0.04953609,0.0239538,-0.01990013,0.00718904,0.10824168,-0.0333264,0.00534452,0.03755045,0.05416176,-0.02527899,-0.0693327,-0.05479585,-0.01918993,0.02705827,-0.01497472,0.05803509,-0.00294247,0.02805381,-0.03336776,0.05759957,0.05209919,0.05116569,0.03630323,-0.00160084,0.00215225,0.0177414,0.02798986,0.02062116,-0.00015395,0.084